# {{ project_name }}

A Databricks Asset Bundle ML project with MLflow training and model registry scaffolded by [dex](https://github.com/yarrib/dex).

## Setup

```bash
uv sync
```

## Project Structure

```
{{ project_name }}/
├── src/{{ project_name }}/    # Training and inference code
{% if include_notebook %}├── notebooks/                 # Databricks notebooks
{% endif %}├── resources/                 # Job definitions
{% if include_serving %}├── serving/                   # Model serving endpoint definition
{% endif %}├── tests/                     # Tests
├── databricks.yml             # Databricks Asset Bundle config
└── pyproject.toml             # Project config
```

## Development

```bash
# Run tests
uv run pytest

# Lint
uv run ruff check .

# Format
uv run ruff format .

# Build wheel
uv build
```

## Deploy

```bash
# Deploy to dev (default target)
databricks bundle deploy

# Run training job
databricks bundle run {{ project_name }}_training_job

{% if include_serving %}# Deploy model serving endpoint
databricks bundle run {{ project_name }}_serving_endpoint

{% endif %}# Deploy to prod
databricks bundle deploy --target prod
```
